OL,5, Liz Truss would prioritise tax cuts    
OL,6, over giving direct payments to every   
OL,7, household to help cover the cost of    
OL,8, rising energy bills, if she were to    
OL,9, become prime minister, a source close  
OL,10, to her has told the BBC.               
OL,12,FReports suggest Ms Truss is considering
OL,13,Fcutting VAT across the board by 5%.    
OL,15,FBut her Tory leadership rival Rishi    
OL,16,FSunak said the government "must provide
OL,17,Fsome direct support" to all.           
OL,19,FAll households are due to receive #400 
OL,20,Foff their energy bills this winter.    
